Hello there, I'm Nikita. I am from Moldova, but have lived in Arizona for the last two decades. My professional background is in the legal field, but I'm also a car enthusiast, and I have a specific interest in electric cars. 

Each vehicle in my fleet isn't just a rental; it's a personal choice- a car I'd happily take for a spin myself. I've learned to take care of everything in my life, and that philosophy extends to my four-wheeled companions.

From zippy electric rides to robust gas guzzlers, my fleet covers all the bases. Whether you're panning a weekend escape, a family road trip, or just need a reliable ride for errands, I've got you covered.

Now, let's talk honesty, cleanliness, and punctuality. These aren't just virtues to me; they're the backbone of my approach. I believe in being upfront about my cars and delivering on time, and I appreciate it when my guests reciprocate with respect for the vehicles I provide.

In a nutshell, I'm not just a Turo host ‚Äì I'm a guy who loves what he does, takes pride in his cars, and wants you to experience the same joy and reliability that I get from them. So, if you're in Arizona and need a set of wheels, hit me up. I've got the keys to your next great drive!

Here is my small fleet of 10 cars (you can also find them by scrolling through my profile):


2017 Chevrolet Bolt (Fully electric - 263 miles of range)
2022 Tesla Model 3 (Fully Electric - 260 miles of range)
2022 Tesla Model Y (7 seats and - 320 miles of range)
2017 VW Tiguan (AWD & 7 seats - regular Gas vehicle)
2017 Chrysler Pacifica (8 seats - comfortable, family)
2016 & 2017 Fiat 500e (limited range electric Car for short distances).

I am originally from a small town in southern Iowa called Osceola where my wife is from Huron, South Dakota.  My wife and I met while both attending pharmacy school at South Dakota State University.  After graduation, we both moved to greater metropolitan Phoenix to begin our pharmacy careers with Walgreens in 2006.  We are both currently employed at Strive Compounding Pharmacy and have many outside interests that keep our family busy.  We both grew up with fathers who were small business owners and mothers who encouraged us to follow our dreams!  Therefore in 2009, we bought our first "house to flip".  We've had a blast flipping houses with many great learning lessons.  Over the years, the outside interests crescendoed into Turo!  I've personally always loved a wide variety of cars.  Turo has given us the opportunity to explore the hobby and offer our favorites back to the ride sharing community.  We work hard to provide a fabulous car coupled with exceptional service.  As you can see, we've strived to maintain a great track record of satisfied clientele!

Hello! I'm thrilled to be a part of the Turo community as a host. My name is Jeremiah, and I take great pride in providing a trustworthy and responsible car rental experience for my guests. Let me share a bit about myself and why you can trust me with your rental needs.

Trustworthiness and responsibility are two qualities that define me both personally and professionally. I understand that when you rent a car, you're not just looking for a means of transportation but also seeking peace of mind. As your host, I aim to deliver that peace of mind through my commitment to reliability, honesty, and exceptional service.

I have built a strong reputation for being trustworthy by consistently maintaining open and transparent communication with my guests. From the initial booking process to the end of your rental period, I am readily available to answer any questions or address any concerns you may have. I believe in fostering a relationship based on trust, ensuring that you have a positive and stress-free experience from start to finish.

Responsibility is another value that is deeply ingrained in me. I understand the importance of taking care of your vehicle and providing a clean and well-maintained rental experience. Before each rental, I personally inspect and ensure that the vehicle is in excellent condition, both mechanically and aesthetically. I adhere to all necessary safety protocols, ensuring that the vehicle meets or exceeds all legal requirements and standards.

Furthermore, I take pride in going the extra mile to accommodate my guests' needs. Whether it's offering flexible pickup and drop-off options, providing helpful travel tips, or assisting with any specific requests, I strive to deliver exceptional customer service. Your satisfaction and comfort are my top priorities, and I am dedicated to making your experience with Turo memorable and enjoyable.

Rest assured, when you choose to rent from me, you're choosing a host who values your trust, takes responsibility seriously, and is committed to providing a top-notch rental experience. I look forward to welcoming you and exceeding your expectations. Let's embark on a journey together with Turo!
